node.text:
Every American should be outraged, disappointed and demand our President step down and resign.  For over 20 years we as Americans have invested so much in Afghanistan… our Troops have sacrificed more than words can describe.  I’ve spoken to hundreds of troops who served and sacrificed in Afghanistan.  I have thanked all of them for their service and listened to countless stories of heroism and bravery.  I am at a loss for words.

This video shows the current situation and how desperate people are to leave their home country of Afghanistan and be with Americans.  These people are so desperate to leave, they are hanging onto departing planes as if a Zombie apocalypse is chasing them.  It is a different apocalypse taking over, one that is worse than death for most. 

There is a right and wrong way to do things.  How we pulled out of Afghanistan was wrong.  This is a full representation of our current administration, they are a disgrace and have made the World less safe for everyone. 

We need to stop focusing on being Politically correct and who we offend. 

We are going backwards, not forward. 

We need strong Men and women to step forward and do what’s right. Not step down and be weak. 

This is all about Politics and back door deals. 

We all need to know what’s happening and be very aware. #thoughts

node.text: Visionaries see things that others do not. Keeping focus on what can be made from nothing isn’t a question. Figuring out how to make it possible lies the challenge. Never give up on your visions. My vision is making a place that is a refuge from all the chaos in the World for my children. A place where I can’t see a single neighbor or hear one car.  And of course a place I can piss and shoot guns off my porch.  That’s my vision. #homestead #montana #peace #mountainlife @triplecreek_builders @cuttingedgeexcavation

node.text:
We may look weak to the rest of the World because of one man’s lack of leadership. But a majority of us Americans are strong, patriotic, proud, traditional, equal and Free. 

We can not let tyranny and politics stop us from expressing and defending our Rights. 

We will NOT COMPLY! #united #thoughts

node.text: My heart yearns to help our stranded fellow Americans in Afghanistan… my hearts breaks for our fallen soldiers and allies.  We need real Leadership.  I’ve said this before, our current administration is not a pro American administration, nor is it a pro Freedom administration.  This administration does not care about us nor our Rights.  We need to hold them accountable and we must protect our people and bring them home! No one left behind!🙏🏻🇺🇸 #thoughts #unacceptable
